Lloyd's List analyst Richard Meade said the Chong Chon Gang's last recorded port call was in Vostochnyy, Russia, where it listed its destination as Havana, Cuba. Before its visit to Russia the ship spent several months visiting Chinese ports, leaving Tianjin on Jan. 25, Meade said in a report Lloyd's List provided to USA TODAY.
